    <h1>Program Option 2: Intensive Coaching & Video Review</h1>
    <p>This is a comprehensive, high-touch retraining program. It includes weekly video feedback, live Skype retraining adjustment sessions, and a dynamically modified exercise program that changes as your hand responds.</p>
    
    <p>We work closely on fine-tuning orthotics, analyzing instrument angle, and introducing specific cognitive and movement hurdles to solidify your progress under pressure. This option is recommended for professional performers aiming for a fast and thorough recovery.</p>

